This directory contains the following files:

-- initialization --

initDemosModule.R -- installs packages required by the scripts listed
below.


-- older demos --

basicDemo.R -- demonstrates a very basic alignment of two hexagons
(requires the main function files manifoldFunctions.R and
visualizationFunctions.R).

quadAlignmentDemo.R -- demonstrates the alignment of two
quadrilaterals (requires the base-model function files
manifoldFunctions.R and visualizationFunctions.R).

quadSequenceDemo.R -- demonstrates the alignment of two quadrilaterals
and the construction of paths over graphs formed from their aligned
representations (requires the base-model function files
manifoldFunctions.R, visualizationFunctions.R, and pathOperations.R).


-- newer demos -- 

quadResponseFieldDemo.R -- demonstrates the construction of several
"response fields" over a quadrilateral data set, and comparison of
them (requires the base-model function files
cognitiveObjectFunctions.R and visualizationFunctions.R).

quadSequenceResponseFieldDemo.R -- demonstrates the construction of
response fields over two quadrilateral data sets, and how they may be
used for manifold alignment (requires the base-model function files
cognitiveObjectFunctions.R, manifoldFunctions.R, pathOperations.R, and
visualizationFunctions.R).


